Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity

Class NoteEntity

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity.NoteEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class NoteEntity extends Object implements Serializable
The NoteEntity class represents the "note" table in the database. Each instance of this class corresponds to a single row in the table.
